data.text: @mkalfus Thank you. I appreciate it. That makes sense about other homes having no impact. If anything I imagine it could even annoy some neighbors nearby to have all the extra foot traffic, vehicles, parking, constant photos, etc...
@SacAppraiser It affected it a lot. HGTV and Lance Bass and others got into a bidding war over it. Buyer's agent says prolly no ripple effect on the non-Brady Bunch homes on that street!
@mkalfus Do you happen to know what otherwise similar-sized homes are selling for in the neighborhood? I'm wondering how much the Brady factor affected the price.
